OL,3,CThree arrested over disappearance of
OL,4,Cman more than 20 years ago
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder as police
OL,8,Finvestigate the disappearance of a man
OL,9,Ftwo decades ago.
OL,11,FRobert Scott Clive, known as 'Scott',
OL,12,Ffrom Stranraer, was last seen shortly
OL,13,Fafter 11pm on October 10 2002 in the
OL,14,FCoronation Street area of North
OL,15,FShields, near Newcastle.
OL,17,FScott was 30 when he disappeared. His
OL,18,Fbody has never been found.
