OL,3,CThree arrested over disappearance of
OL,4,Cman more than 20 years ago
OL,6,FTwo men - aged in their 40s and 50s -
OL,7,Fand a woman in her 40s have been
OL,8,Farrested, according to Northumbria
OL,9,FPolice, the force leading the
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FThey remain in custody while enquiries
OL,13,Fare ongoing.
OL,15,FOfficers searched an address in the
OL,16,Farea of North Shields where Scott was
OL,17,Flast seen.
OL,19,FThe current occupant, who moved in
OL,20,Fafter 2002, has been found alternative
OL,21,Faccommodation in the meantime.
