OL,3,CThree arrested over disappearance of
OL,4,Cman more than 20 years ago
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mark Atherton from
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police said: "We are doing
OL,8,Feverything we can to provide Scott's
OL,9,Ffamily with the answers they deserve.
OL,11,F"Upon receiving new information, we
OL,12,Fhave taken the decision to arrest two
OL,13,Fmen and a woman in relation to Scott's
OL,14,Fdisappearance.
OL,16,F"They remain in custody while our
OL,17,Fenquiries are ongoing."
OL,19,FHe added: "We still believe there
OL,20,Fcould be key information that people
OL,21,Fknow in the local community
